  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study estimate VTE incidence. Investigators prospectively record all cases of
      symptomatic pulmonary embolism (PE) and deep vein thrombosis (DVT) of the lower limbs
      diagnosed between March 1, 2013 and February 28, 2014 in hospitals and in the community.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
