  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Gathering information about potential factors predisposing Thromboembolic disease and treatments undertaken.</measure>
    <time_frame>two years after VTE</time_frame>
    <description>After two years, all medication given to the patient to treat his initial VTE will be recorded, as well as the ongoing of thromboembolic disease</description>
  </primary_outcome>
